        <header><h1>Web Router Examples</h1></header><div class="container"><aside><!--$--><web-widget name="Menu"><ul class="menu"><li><a href="/">🏠</a></li><li><a href="/react-server-component">React: Server component</a></li><li><a href="/vue3-server-component">Vue3: Server component</a></li><li><a href="/dynamic-routes/@web-widget">Dynamic routes</a></li><li><a href="/react-and-vue">Using react and vue together</a></li><li><a href="/vue-module-css">Vue CSS Modules</a></li><li><a href="/custom-handlers">Custom handlers</a></li><li><a href="/client-only-component">Client only component</a></li><li><a href="/css-lazy-dynamic">CSS: lazy chunk (dynamic import)</a></li><li><a href="/fetching-data">Fetching data</a></li><li><a href="/style">Styling</a></li><li><a href="/large-css">Large CSS (external link)</a></li><li><a href="/meta">Meta</a></li><li><a href="/form">Form submissions</a></li><li><a href="/fallback">Error handling</a></li><li><a href="/react-streaming">React: Streaming</a></li><li><a href="/vue3-streaming">Vue3: Streaming</a></li><li><a href="/experimental-async-component">Async component</a></li><li><a href="/background-tasks">Background tasks</a></li><li><a href="/vue3-router">Using vue3 router</a></li><li><a href="/vue2-router">Using vue2 router</a></li><li><a href="/react-import-widgets">React: Import vue2 and vue3</a></li><li><a href="/vue3-import-widgets">Vue3: Import react and vue2</a></li><li><a href="/vue2-import-widgets">Vue2: Import react and vue3</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="/vue2-server-component">Vue2: Server component</a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="/lit-html-template"> Lit html template </a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="/api/hello-world"> Api route </a></li></ul></web-widget><!--/$--></aside><main><div class="showcase"><h2>Large CSS Showcase</h2><p>This page imports more than 8 KB of CSS. The build pipeline keeps it as an external stylesheet (<code>&lt;link&gt;</code>) rather than inlining it into a <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> tag. View source to verify.</p><hr class="divider"/><div class="grid"><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Card component</h3><p class="card-text">A card with hover effect, shadow, and rounded corners.</p><div class="card-footer"><span class="badge badge-primary">New</span><span class="badge badge-success">Active</span></div></div><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Badges</h3><p class="card-text">Colored badges for status indicators.</p><div class="card-footer"><span class="badge badge-primary">Primary</span><span class="badge badge-success">Success</span><span class="badge badge-danger">Danger</span><span class="badge badge-warning">Warning</span><span class="badge badge-info">Info</span></div></div><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Progress bars</h3><p class="card-text">Animated progress indicators.</p><div class="progress"><div class="progress-bar progress-bar-primary" style="width:75%"></div></div><div class="progress"><div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" style="width:90%"></div></div></div></div><div class="grid"><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Buttons</h3><p class="card-text">Various button styles.</p><div class="card-footer"><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Primary</a><a href="#" class="btn btn-success">Success</a><a href="#" class="btn btn-danger">Danger</a><a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">Outline</a></div></div><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Alerts</h3><div class="alert alert-success">Operation completed successfully.</div><div class="alert alert-danger">An error occurred.</div><div class="alert alert-warning">Please review your input.</div><div class="alert alert-info">Here is some information.</div></div><div class="card"><h3 class="card-title">Stats</h3><div class="stat" style="margin-bottom:12px"><div class="stat-icon">★</div><div><div class="stat-value">12,345</div><div class="stat-label">Total stars</div></div></div><div class="stat"><div class="stat-icon" style="background:var(--color-success)"